title: Group Therapy: They're ALWAYS Snobby & Stuck Up
description: Alisha and her husband run a tech company and are doing very well for themselves. However, they've been needing to get out and network with people who are also doing well for themselves and they don't like how they talk to people. They're rude to servers, make fun of poor people, always talking about their money, etc.
